{
  "video_id": "i63jTStjZSQ",
  "title": "Gabriel Barcia-Colombo: Capturing memories in video art",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 15260.0,
      "text": "Translator: Thu-Huong Ha Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16288.0,
      "end_time": 18447.0,
      "text": "I love to collect things."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18447.0,
      "end_time": 20436.0,
      "text": "Ever since I was a kid, I&#39;ve had massive collections"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20437.0,
      "end_time": 23166.0,
      "text": "of random stuff, everything from bizarre hot sauces"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23166.0,
      "end_time": 26404.0,
      "text": "from all around the world to insects"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26404.0,
      "end_time": 28808.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve captured and put in jars."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28808.0,
      "end_time": 30845.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s no secret, because I like collecting things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30845.0,
      "end_time": 32781.0,
      "text": "that I love the Natural History Museum"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32781.0,
      "end_time": 34181.0,
      "text": "and the collections of animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34181.0,
      "end_time": 35995.0,
      "text": "at the Natural History Museum in dioramas."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35996.0,
      "end_time": 38133.0,
      "text": "These, to me, are like living sculptures, right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38133.0,
      "end_time": 39550.0,
      "text": "that you can go and look at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39550.0,
      "end_time": 41285.0,
      "text": "and they memorialize a specific point of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41285.0,
      "end_time": 42931.0,
      "text": "in this animal&#39;s life."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42932.0,
      "end_time": 44814.0,
      "text": "So I was thinking about my own life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44814.0,
      "end_time": 46727.0,
      "text": "and how I&#39;d like to memorialize my life, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46727.0,
      "end_time": 49510.0,
      "text": "for the ages, and also — (Laughter) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49510.0,
      "end_time": 51997.0,
      "text": "the lives of my friends, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51997.0,
      "end_time": 54613.0,
      "text": "the problem with this is that my friends aren&#39;t quite keen"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54613.0,
      "end_time": 57789.0,
      "text": "on the idea of me taxidermy-ing them. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57789.0,
      "end_time": 60492.0,
      "text": "So instead, I turned to video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60492.0,
      "end_time": 62790.0,
      "text": "and video is the next best way to preserve and memorialize"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62790.0,
      "end_time": 65564.0,
      "text": "someone and to capture a specific moment in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65564.0,
      "end_time": 67741.0,
      "text": "So what I did was, I filmed six of my friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 67741.0,
      "end_time": 70141.0,
      "text": "and then, using video mapping and video projection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70141.0,
      "end_time": 72622.0,
      "text": "I created a video sculpture, which was these six friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72622.0,
      "end_time": 76564.0,
      "text": "projected into jars. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76564.0,
      "end_time": 78277.0,
      "text": "So now I have this collection of my friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78278.0,
      "end_time": 80670.0,
      "text": "I can take around with me whenever I go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80670.0,
      "end_time": 81979.0,
      "text": "and this is called Animalia Chordata,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81979.0,
      "end_time": 83795.0,
      "text": "from the Latin nomenclature for"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83796.0,
      "end_time": 85956.0,
      "text": "human being, classification system."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 85956.0,
      "end_time": 88918.0,
      "text": "So this piece memorializes my friends in these jars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 88918.0,
      "end_time": 93277.0,
      "text": "and they actually move around. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93277.0,
      "end_time": 95370.0,
      "text": "So, this is interesting to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95370.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "but it lacked a certain human element. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101820.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a digital sculpture, so I wanted to add"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101820.0,
      "end_time": 102693.0,
      "text": "an interaction system. So what I did was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102694.0,
      "end_time": 104477.0,
      "text": "I added a proximity sensor, so that when you get close"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104477.0,
      "end_time": 106636.0,
      "text": "to the people in jars, they react to you in different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 106636.0,
      "end_time": 108363.0,
      "text": "You know, just like people on the street"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 108363.0,
      "end_time": 110219.0,
      "text": "when you get too close to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 110219.0,
      "end_time": 112804.0,
      "text": "Some people reacted in terror. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112805.0,
      "end_time": 114818.0,
      "text": "Others reacted in asking you for help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 114818.0,
      "end_time": 118316.0,
      "text": "and some people hide from you."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 118316.0,
      "end_time": 119947.0,
      "text": "So this was really interesting to me, this idea of"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 119947.0,
      "end_time": 122820.0,
      "text": "taking video off the screen and putting it in real life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 122820.0,
      "end_time": 124329.0,
      "text": "and also adding interactivity to sculpture."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124329.0,
      "end_time": 128394.0,
      "text": "So over the next year, I documented 40 of my other friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 128394.0,
      "end_time": 130226.0,
      "text": "and trapped them in jars as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 130226.0,
      "end_time": 132171.0,
      "text": "and created a piece known as Garden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 132171.0,
      "end_time": 134523.0,
      "text": "which is literally a garden of humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 134523.0,
      "end_time": 136667.0,
      "text": "But something about the first piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 136667.0,
      "end_time": 138572.0,
      "text": "the Animali Chordata piece, kept coming back to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 138572.0,
      "end_time": 140393.0,
      "text": "this idea of interaction with art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 140393.0,
      "end_time": 142715.0,
      "text": "and I really liked the idea of people being able to interact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 142715.0,
      "end_time": 145400.0,
      "text": "and also being challenged by interacting with art."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 145400.0,
      "end_time": 146858.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to create a new piece that actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 146859.0,
      "end_time": 148748.0,
      "text": "forced people to come and interact with something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148748.0,
      "end_time": 150447.0,
      "text": "and the way I did this was actually by projecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 150447.0,
      "end_time": 154827.0,
      "text": "a 1950s housewife into a blender. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154827.0,
      "end_time": 157322.0,
      "text": "This is a piece called Blend, and what it does is"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 157322.0,
      "end_time": 159185.0,
      "text": "it actually makes you implicit in the work of art."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159185.0,
      "end_time": 161526.0,
      "text": "You may never experience the entire thing yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161526.0,
      "end_time": 163850.0,
      "text": "You can walk away, you can just watch as this character"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 163850.0,
      "end_time": 166275.0,
      "text": "stands there in the blender and looks at you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 166275.0,
      "end_time": 168349.0,
      "text": "or you can actually choose to interact with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 168349.0,
      "end_time": 172482.0,
      "text": "So if you do choose to interact with the piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 172482.0,
      "end_time": 174642.0,
      "text": "and you press the blender button, it actually sends"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174642.0,
      "end_time": 178730.0,
      "text": "this character into this dizzying disarray of dishevelment."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 178740.0,
      "end_time": 181626.0,
      "text": "By doing that, you are now part of my piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 181626.0,
      "end_time": 183658.0,
      "text": "You, like the people that are trapped in my work"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183658.0,
      "end_time": 187719.0,
      "text": "— (Blender noises, laughter) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 187719.0,
      "end_time": 194826.0,
      "text": "have become part of my work as well. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 194826.0,
      "end_time": 197190.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 197190.0,
      "end_time": 199442.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 199442.0,
      "end_time": 203820.0,
      "text": "But, but this seems a bit unfair, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 203820.0,
      "end_time": 205594.0,
      "text": "I put my friends in jars, I put this character,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 205594.0,
      "end_time": 208411.0,
      "text": "this sort of endangered species character in a blender."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 208411.0,
      "end_time": 210411.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;d never done anything about myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 210411.0,
      "end_time": 212123.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d never really memorialized myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 212123.0,
      "end_time": 214393.0,
      "text": "So I decided to create a piece which is a self-portrait piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 214393.0,
      "end_time": 216618.0,
      "text": "This is sort of a self-portrait taxidermy time capsule piece"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 216618.0,
      "end_time": 218865.0,
      "text": "called A Point Just Passed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 218865.0,
      "end_time": 221497.0,
      "text": "in which I project myself on top of a time card punch clock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 221497.0,
      "end_time": 223201.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s up to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223201.0,
      "end_time": 225147.0,
      "text": "If you want to choose to punch that punch card clock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 225147.0,
      "end_time": 226853.0,
      "text": "you actually age me."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 226854.0,
      "end_time": 229410.0,
      "text": "So I start as a baby, and then if you punch the clock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 229410.0,
      "end_time": 234720.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll actually transform the baby into a toddler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 234720.0,
      "end_time": 237303.0,
      "text": "and then from a toddler I&#39;m transformed into a teenager."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 237303.0,
      "end_time": 239823.0,
      "text": "From a teenager, I&#39;m transformed into my current self."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 239823.0,
      "end_time": 242911.0,
      "text": "From my current self, I&#39;m turned into a middle-aged man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242911.0,
      "end_time": 246770.0,
      "text": "and then, from there, into an elderly man."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 246770.0,
      "end_time": 249702.0,
      "text": "And if you punch the punch card clock a hundred times"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 249702.0,
      "end_time": 252773.0,
      "text": "in one day, the piece goes black"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 252773.0,
      "end_time": 255466.0,
      "text": "and is not to be reset until the next day."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 255466.0,
      "end_time": 257550.0,
      "text": "So, in doing so, you&#39;re erasing time."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 257550.0,
      "end_time": 259478.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re actually implicit in this work"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 259478.0,
      "end_time": 261483.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re erasing my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 261483.0,
      "end_time": 263630.0,
      "text": "So I like this about interactive video sculpture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 263630.0,
      "end_time": 265207.0,
      "text": "that you can actually interact with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 265207.0,
      "end_time": 267790.0,
      "text": "that all of you can actually touch an artwork"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 267790.0,
      "end_time": 268943.0,
      "text": "and be part of the artwork yourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 268943.0,
      "end_time": 271414.0,
      "text": "and hopefully, one day, I&#39;ll have each and every one of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 271414.0,
      "end_time": 273574.0,
      "text": "trapped in one of my jars. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 273574.0,
      "end_time": 278665.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}